description: Flip ‘N’ Chop because it’s Coralville’s one-stop-shop for the flavors of the world!This cool blue truck supplies Iowa with all the global cuisine it needs with its deliciously eclectic mobile menu. Here are just a few of the places you can send your taste buds off to:China! When you order up their scrumptious "Crispy Skin Pork Belly Steam Bun"Mexico! If you go for the succulently rich "Chicken Adobo & Rice"India! When you get beautiful "Bombay Potatoes with Saffron Basmati Rice" in your bellySo be sure to pop on by to Flip ‘N’ Chop, because it absolutely is the top truck to try.
name: Flip 'N' Chop
